      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WHITE DRESS (8) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (18.02) at this track in a Maiden. Has first look at box 8 this time. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Good form should continue. COUNTERPART (7) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (18.13) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. JUST A GLANCE (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Ice Queen Kaos (18.08) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Winning chance. FAB PRINCE (1) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
